lead_paragraph: One of the most dramatic drafts in NFL history wrapped up in Chicago on Saturday with the team that started the spectacle ahead of schedule by trading the No. 1 overall pick to the Los Angeles Rams two weeks earlier.

headline.print_headline: Draft Ends With Titans Naming 253rd Pick
